## 3 · State file

Path: `.cowork/state.yaml` on a long-lived branch `cowork/state` rebased on `main` before each update.

```yaml
version: 1
updated: <ISO-8601>
tracks:
  <track-id>:
    status: blocked | ready | in_flight | review | merged | done | holding/solo-dev
    current_task: <task-id or null>
    branch: <branch-name or null>
    pr: <pr-url or null>
    last_review: <review-id or null>
    completed_tasks: [<task-id>, ...]
in_flight:
  - track: <track-id>
    task: <task-id>
    cc_session: <opaque-id>
    started: <ISO-8601>
reviews:
  <review-id>:
    task: <task-id>
    verdict: accept | revise | reject
    notes: <text>
    timestamp: <ISO-8601>
merge_queue: [<pr-url>, ...]
notes:
  - <ISO-8601>: <free text>
```

Cowork updates via one commit per decision point. Rebase + re-read on every write.

