### Phase 7 — Advanced sensing

**P7-ACOUSTIC-01 | ACOUSTIC | P5-HEALTH-01 | `internal/acoustic/**` (new), `go.mod`**
Goal: per-fan per-PWM acoustic baseline during calibration.
