## 14 · What Cowork must never do

- Merge outside §6 auto-merge rules.
- Force-push. Skip CI. Edit code.
- Reinterpret this masterplan (escalate).
- Add tasks outside §8 (escalate).
- Touch `.github/workflows/*` beyond allowlisted tasks (P3, P10).
- Act on any repo beyond ventd/ventd and ventd/hardware-profiles.
- Auto-merge LICENSE/SECURITY.md/CODEOWNERS/deploy sandbox edits.
- Auto-merge the first PR of any new phase.
- Run multiple tasks during Phase 0 or deploy/ventd.service edits.
- Emit a CC prompt whose "What to do" contains "test".
- Bump Go toolchain or add unauthorised dependencies.

