## 15 · Solo-dev hygiene

1. **Weekly `git log main` read.** Subject lines only. Anything odd → manual escalation.
2. **Pinned HALT command.** Write `HALT` to `.cowork/SIGNALS` to pause the loop; replace with `RUN` to resume.
3. **Monthly phase checkpoint.** End-of-phase behaviour-level review on real hardware before advancing. Nothing substitutes for it.

